== Egg Bites ==

MICROWAVE: Open plastic packaging slightly to vent. With @Red Pepper and Swiss Egg White Bites{6}(plastic packaging) in packaging, microwave until heated through, ~{40-60%seconds}.

TOASTER OVEN: Preheat #toaster oven{} to 350 degrees. Remove @Spinach & Feta Egg Bites{6}(plastic packaging) from packaging and place in toaster oven. Cook until heated through, ~{5-10%minutes}.

== Muffins ==

@Blueberry Muffin{2} and @Chocolate Chip Muffin{2}: Enjoy!

== Belgian Waffles ==

Heat a #waffle iron{}. Add @Belgian Waffle{2} to iron. Warm for about ~{30%seconds}.

TOASTER OR OVEN: Heat #toaster{} or #traditional oven{} to low. Add waffle to toaster or oven. Warm for about ~{1%minute}.

MICROWAVE: Microwave waffle for ~{20%seconds}.

== Latte ==

Serve @La Colombe Vanilla Oat Lattes{7} over ice and enjoy!

> Not a morning person? We hear you! This bundle of vegetarian faves makes breakfast easier and significantly more delicious: hearty red pepper and cheese plus spinach and feta sous-vide egg bites, blueberry and chocolate chip muffins with pillowy tops and a moist crumb, Belgian waffles warm up quickly in the microwave or toaster—a decadent treat in a flash. And a creamy, ready-to-drink, low-sugar, vanilla oat milk latte—all you have to do is crack open a can!